        ></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 py-20 md:py-32">

          <!-- Title Only - Left Side With Padding -->
          <div class="px-6 md:px-12 lg:pl-[12%] animate-fade-in-up" style="opacity: 0;">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">
              App for iOS · macOS · Playdate
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-[0.9] tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">
              <span class="font-extralight">Chaos</span><br/><span class="font-bold">Studies</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base mt-4 max-w-xs font-light">
              Explore strange attractors through touch, sound, and motion.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Description Section -->
      <div class="px-6 md:px-12 py-12 border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-xl">
            Strange attractors are mathematical patterns that emerge from chaotic systems. Though governed by simple equations, they never repeat exactly, creating infinitely complex, beautiful shapes.
          </p>
